Steps to Reproduce Updated: Search user in AIC and try reports

What We've Learned Updated: Error message when trying to search user and view reports:
Sorry we are unable to complete this request right now, the application log file may contain helpful troubleshooting information.

url: /v2/admins/data/audit/reports/trustee/memberof
status: 500

It was believed that this issue was fixed in 11.6 so we upgraded from 11.5, but the issue persists
Next Steps Updated: R&D review logs
Next Steps Updated: Dev team identified a fix and is actively working on it. Will update when fix is available.
